precis:
Enactment of the WTO TECHNICAL AMENDMENTS ORDER, NO. 4 which amends and
introduces supplementary Chapter Notes in Schedule I to the Customs Tariff
to account for the delayed implementation of amendments pursuant to the
WTO Agreement relating to specified cereals and cereal products.
